data.description: End Unit townhome!  Two bedrooms with a large living area.   Kitchen has updated Black and SS appliances. The flooring is tile in the lower living areas and carpet in the upstairs bedrooms.  Fantastic especially if you plan to use as investment property.   There is a small yard off the patio with views of an open field.  Located in Carolina Forest, not only convenient to Camp Lejeune but also many restaurants, shopping centers and entertainment venues.  Call today for and appointment!
